Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost...there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's School is supposed\Nto be amazing inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity says there's never\Nbeen a school like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the students get to\Ndo tons of awesome stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like...A BROOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And a dustpan...\NAnd some buckets...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Try another window!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whooooo's ready for cupcakes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh they're not for you, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're for sharing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First, say something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocellus, you are\Na great listener!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you get to\Nkeep one cupcake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and share one with\Nanother creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona, you're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right students, it's time\Nto meet some new friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's friendship\Nin action, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! And I thought\Nour school was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Miss Cheerilee never\Nlets us play buckball in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I've tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go here instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] What could be better\Nthan learning friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with your best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning friendship with\Nyour best friends and CAKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we're going to\Nlearn about friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,through the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike? Slide one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the days of\NChancellor Puddinghead--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Still getting used\Nto my new wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was saying... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Nthree doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanna go to\Nyour school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to learn\Nfriendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And play Buckball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you\Nthree come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike? You're in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you could use a\Nguidance counsellor's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hint. Hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Great....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just go dust my office\Nfor the seventieth time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have\Nto tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but... you can't be\Nmy students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this place\Nfor EVERY creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But we teach\Nfriendship lessons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know all about\Nhelping ponies in need
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and being there\Nfor each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just give\Nus a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You need Cheerilee's\Nclasses, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! You don't want late\Nmarks on your permanent record!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All: O dragon, my dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike..? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not\Ngiving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can prove we\Nbelong in this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Um, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By showing Twilight we've\Nstill got lots to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know just\Nwhere to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know better than to leave\Nour good tools out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And aren't you supposed to\Nbe on harvest duty right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, it's not like the apples\Nare going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those chores are\Nyour responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Farm work is family work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, if I went to\NTwilight's School,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd learn to be better\Nat helping the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So that's what\Nthis is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's\Nlearning you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to give you a\Nprivate lesson right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with cleanin'\Nup all this equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please can I go to\NTwilight's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call\Nyou Repeatie Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So there I was, leading the\NWonderbolt formation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,into a super-dangerous sundog\Nspiral, when suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a HUGE storm\Ncloud in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My genius happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed the\Nroutine on the fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And because my crew are such\Ntight friends, they followed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] What did you do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the coolest thing ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I flew up-\N-and did a super-amazing half twist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,into a backflip sonic rainboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I never told that story\Nto my students before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,SCOOTALOO..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Never met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch where you are going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching, watching\Nyou drive like a crazy pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe if you did not drop\Napples all over the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've never seen Apple Bloom\Nand Scootaloo argue like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they usually go together\Nlike candy canes and stripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your\Nfault, Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sweetie Belle\Nis the clumsy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking to either\None of you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! They\Nseem really upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like they\Nforgot they're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good plan, Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you who is\Nthe one who is careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And great acting,\NSweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're an awesome team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\NPinkie Pie: Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're friends again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy cane stripes forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they'll never let us\Ninto Twilight's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we've tried shirkin'\Nchores, pesterin',
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,disguises, fightin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. We need to\Ndo something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't tried crying yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It always\Nworks for Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's coming\Nfrom outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, she looks so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We better go see what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having real trouble with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the School of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight won't let\Nyou go either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in her class but\N[sob] it's too HARD!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just moved here\Nto go to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but everything's so\Nnew and different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sweetie\NBelle and Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Cutie\NMark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniff] I'm Cozy Glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very nice to\Nmeet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know\Nif I'll stay long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably flunk out; I'm\Nhaving so much trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with my friendship lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can help with those!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We know all about friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And studying with you\Nwould be almost as good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as being in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how\Nfriendship works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you give from your heart,\Nyou don't expect anything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, golly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use some help\Nwith my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something nice\Nfor each of these ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know\Nanything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's so hard to talk\Nto ponies you've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause we know all\Nthose ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for a\Nfriendship A plus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Bon Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna do\Nsomething nice for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,first you gotta figure\Nout what she needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed\Nto do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is about\Nlistening to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh. That cactus\Nkeeps pricking her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,every step she takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. If only there was something to\Nprotect her from those spines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you need\Nhelp carrying your cactus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so here's a safe way\Nto take it home. [giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh, next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe don't give away my helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Green. Purple. Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaand one more purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew. Sorting all those took\Nlonger than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think Mrs. Cake will\Nlike these new sprinkle shakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm! Now she won't have to use\Nrainbow sprinkles all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She can just pick\Nthe color she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, I\Nwas out to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you fillies\Nwaiting for me long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Um. These\Nare for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh well, what a lovely surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to try them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I made rainbow sprinkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But...she...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At least she likes\Nher present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly! How'd you know that\Nwould make him so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship means pitching in to\Nhelp others' chores go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Specially when their special\Nsomepony's waiting for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That class was sooo boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Miss Cheerilee\Ncan make the history
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of radishes exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they don't have to\Nlearn about that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,at Twilight's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an A on my homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\NNice goin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never could have\Ndone it without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wish we\Ncould've done more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmare Twilight is\Ngiving us a big test
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could really use\Nyour help studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to go to Twilight's\Nschool more than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but helping you has\Nbeen even more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it.... control?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness, loyalty, honesty,\Ngenerosity, laughter, magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!\NWoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd the test go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there essay\Nquestions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you remember\Nwhat we taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I......... FAILED!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could Cozy Glow\Nfail her friendship test?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see you\Nthree in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we wanted to\Nbe invited inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but it kinda went\Ndifferent in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd\Ndo something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Like.. what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You ARE Cozy Glow's\Ntutors, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been working\Nwith her for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been setting\Nher up to fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How?      What?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're upset that I\Nwon't let you come to my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But to teach Cozy all the\Nwrong things out of spite,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we taught her\Nall the right things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain these\Nfriendship test answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the six\Nelements of harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Five turtlenecks\Nand a cheese grater?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the Princess\Nof Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't understand....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you three\Nwould pull such a mean prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm going\Nto have to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay away from\Nmy school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[sarcastic] Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll alphabetize\Nthem in reverse order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Not much need for\Na guidance counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at a School of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow: Ahem!\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How much of that\Ndid you hear!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get you a comfort pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Security blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Empathy cocoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, I have\Nplenty of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anecdotes, insight,\Nmidnight confessions...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Go ahead. I'm... listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I got my\Nfriends in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They helped me study for my\Nfriendship test and I failed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. Why would you do that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.... sorry, listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Cutie Mark Crusaders\Nwanted to go to this school
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought if I showed\NHeadmare Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,they're bad at friendship, she'd\Nlet them come here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's devious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I still have a lot\Nto learn about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think\Nyou're doing all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that was a\Nreally, really bad way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to help\Nyour friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what matters\Nis, you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason the Cutie Mark\NCrusaders don't go to this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,school is that they'd make\Nbetter teachers than students!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you DO have a\Nplace for them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. I bet there's no Wonderful\NWorld of Cleaning lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,at Twilight's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never find out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't get how\NCozy failed her test
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,after all that studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how Twilight could\Nblame us for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how gum can be so sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt,\NMiss Cheerilee,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but can I borrow Apple Bloom,\NSweetie Belle, and Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't do anything\Nwrong, we promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I wanted\Nto talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. So we're\Nnot in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow, is there\Nsomething you'd like to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up my\Ntest on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so we could all go\Nto school together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Cozy Glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honesty is one of the\Npillars of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But you already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'd like\Nto give you these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're honorary diplomas,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,making y'all official\Ngraduates of this here school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've more than\Nearned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even\Nhaving to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We are grad-u-ates!\NWe are grad-u-ates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if you're interested, I\Nthink Starlight has a place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for you at my school after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NWooo hooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use some good\Nfriendship tutors on staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear you're\Nthe best out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what're we\Nwaiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get tutoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Cozy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And THAT's why this school needs\Nyou as our guidance counselor.
